 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Bucharest University of Economic Studies[152]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the University of Agronomic Sciences and Veterinary Medicine[153]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Dimitrie Cantemir Christian University[154]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Politehnica University of Bucharest[155]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the University of Pitești[156]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the University of Bucharest[157]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Victor Babeș University of Medicine and Pharmacy, Timișoara[158]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Polytechnic University of Timișoara[159]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the University of Agricultural Sciences and Veterinary Medicine of Cluj-Napoca[160]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Carol I National Defence University[161]
 Romania: Honorary Degree of the Alexandru Ioan Cuza University[162]

Foreign awards

 Czech Republic: Honorary Citizen of the City of Kromeriz[163]
 United Kingdom: Freeman of the City of London[164]
 United Kingdom: Liveryman of the Worshipful Company of Wax Chandlers[165]

Ancestry
As a great-great-grandson of Queen Victoria, through both of his parents, Michael is a third cousin of Queen Margrethe II of Denmark, King Harald V of Norway, King Juan Carlos I of Spain, King Carl XVI Gustav of Sweden and Queen Elizabeth II.


