 Proven Solutions That Work
The products and treatments shown above ARE intended to prevent, treat and cure soft tissue injuries, chronic conditions, and their related pain.  The products above ARE FDA Registered medical devices.
        




King Brand Healthcare Products® is a company dedicated to the development and manufacture of Premium Therapeutic healthcare products. These products represent the Best Design and utilize the most recent advancements in treatment technology.
King Brand® started with one main focus: to help our customers get the best medical treatment possible while in the comfort of their own home. It's our Quality Products and Exceptional Customer Service that make the difference. Helping customers get back on the road to a full, speedy recovery.   
King Brand® products can be found in hospitals, therapy clinics, doctors' offices, and pro athlete training centers worldwide. As an FDA Registered Medical Company, our medical devices are guaranteed to provide you with the therapeutic treatment needed to heal your injury.    
Take some time to browse through our site. You can find all the infomation you need to treat your injury. If you have any questions or need treatment advice, we have a dedicated team of Advisors ready to help assist you. 



 

