About
Dr. Michael King, MD is a Doctor primarily located in White Plains, NY, with other offices in Stamford, CT and Stamford, CT (and 1 other location). He has 21 years of experience. His specialties include Diagnostic Radiology and Radiology.                    Dr. King is affiliated with                            White Plains Hospital Center,                            Stamford Hospital, The, Stamford CT and                            Stamford Hospital.
                 He speaks English.



